# AUTHOR: andree <andreek@tzi.de>
#
# INSTALL
#
#   Install nodejs (v0.4.12) and npm:
#
#     https://github.com/joyent/node/wiki/Installation 
# 
#   Install libs:
#
#     npm install 
#
# CONFIG
#   
#   For persisting you need a redis-server: http://redis.io 
#
#   Start a redis server and set persist in conf.json
#   Editing connection details see persist.js ;-)
#   
# USAGE
#
#   node app.js
#
# TESTS
#
#   ./node_modules/expresso/bin/expresso tests/units/models/* tests/units/* tests/integrations/* 
#
